Access Control List:

If we want to give access to other user then we will use setfacl command:

To modify or assign rights to a user:
setfacl -m u:huma:rw mylove.txt

To remove:
setfacl -x u:huma:rw mylove.txt

For group:
setfacl -m g:IT:r mylove.txt

To assign full rights to another user:
setfacl -R -m u:tahir:rwx /home/taha (-R for recurssive)

